{% comment %}
  Quantity Discount Snippet
  ========================
  Include this snippet in your product template (e.g., product.liquid or
  main-product.liquid) to render quantity discount tiers for the current product.

  Usage:
    {% render 'quantity-discount' %}

  This snippet loads the CSS and JS assets and renders the section that
  contains the configuration. Make sure you have also added the
  quantity-discount-settings.liquid section to your theme's sections/ folder
  and configured tiers via the Shopify theme editor (Customize > Product page).
{% endcomment %}

{% comment %} Load assets once per page {% endcomment %}
{% unless quantity_discount_loaded %}
  {{ 'quantity-discount.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}
  <script src="{{ 'quantity-discount.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
  {% assign quantity_discount_loaded = true %}
{% endunless %}

{% comment %}
  Render the section.
  The section file (quantity-discount-settings.liquid) provides the theme editor
  schema and serializes the tier configuration as JSON.
{% endcomment %}
{% section 'quantity-discount-settings' %}
